                                                        <%= address.FullName %>
                                                    </h5>
                                                    <p class="card-text">
                                                        <strong>Mobile:</strong>
                                                        <%= address.MobileNo %><br>
                                                            <strong>Address:</strong>
                                                            <%= address.FlatNo %>, <%= address.Address %>, <%=
                                                                        address.Landmark %>, <%= address.City %>, <%=
                                                                                address.District %>, <%= address.State
                                                                                    %>, <%= address.Country %>, <%=
                                                                                            address.Pincode %><br>
                                                                                            <strong>Address
                                                                                                Type:</strong>
                                                                                            <%= address.AddressType %>
